faithful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sincere"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honest advice, eager,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"striving, to rectify,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amend, the state of him to whom that advice is given."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A_in~a Al$~afiyqa bisuwo'i ZanK muwlaEN"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily the affectionate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the very affectionate"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is addicted to evil opinion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a prov., applied in the case of the man who fears, for his friend, the accidents of fortune, by reason of his excessive"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afaqap","text_ar":"شَفَقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or affection, &c.]. (TA.) And it is said in the Kur [xxi. 50],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wahumo mina","text_ar":"وَهُمْ مِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ls~aAEapi mu$ofiquwna","text_ar":"ا@لسَّاعَةِ مُشْفِقُونَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And who are fearful of the time of the resurrection"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; the signification of fear being most apparent when"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$ofiqN","text_ar":"مُشْفِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is thus trans. by means of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) See also an instance of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$ofiqN","text_ar":"مُشْفِقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in a similar sense] in the first paragraph of this art."}],"source_refs":["Msb","M","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}